INSERT INTO `mac_vod` VALUES('13397','看动画学习交通安全知识','','kandonghuaxuexijiaotonganquanzhishi','K','','http://i0.letvimg.com/lc07_isvrs/201604/12/17/31/d3347b35-7e0f-4b77-a280-83f53d7d7191.jpg','[db:缩略图]','[db:幻灯图]','','','[db:tag]','乐视高清','其他地区','国语','0','4','',',165,','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','0','60192','0','0','0','0','0','0','6.0','0','486','1480878955','1482263238','0','0','《变形警车珀利 交通安全篇》是由韩国ROI VISUAL、现代汽车和EBS电视台共同推进的全球性儿童交通安全社会贡献活动，旨在增加儿童的交通安全知识、提高社会的交通安全意识。动画历经7年的构思创作，现已进入韩、法、日、俄、中国台湾等二十多个国家和地区，并以其精致明快的3D画面、鲜活生动的人物形象、丰富有趣的故事情节和深入浅出的知识讲解，博得了广大儿童的喜爱。2013年8月10日，《变形警车珀利》在中央电视台少儿频道“金龟子城堡”节目播出，正式和中国大陆的小朋友们见面。《变形警车珀利》的故事发生在布鲁姆斯小镇，警车珀利、救护车安芭、消防车罗伊和直升飞机海利组成了救援队，保护着镇上人民的平安幸福的生活。凯文和多奇是两个活泼淘气的小学男生，经常因为不遵守交通规则陷入麻烦，幸好每一次都有救援队的大家出手相助。随着故事的发展，他们也会逐渐学会交通安全知识和做人的道理。','letv','','','http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535177.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535201.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535217.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535233.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535245.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535259.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535275.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535291.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535312.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535333.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535360.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535372.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535392.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535403.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535413.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535427.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535438.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535452.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535462.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535476.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535488.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535499.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535521.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535540.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535553.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535569.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay/25535595.html#http://www.letv.com/ptv/vplay